Container is a snapshot
Image is a snapshot

COMMANDS
ps: list containers (made w/docker run, use start/stop/ps)
images: list images (made w/docker commit -m "message" -t elliotw/tag)
run: create container from image (run -p 6371 -i -t ewinard/tag /usr/bin/mongo)
start/stop: stop a container
build: create an image from a Dockerfile
inspect: inspect an image
logs: review stdout/stderr from container
push/pull: push to docker (or your index)

# get tree/thin container
$ ps xwf

# attach to the running linux container
lxc-attach -n ...

# build the docker
$ docker build -t elliotw/docker.io.lecture .
